com.revature.sms.domain

  • Packages that use com.revature.sms.domain 
    Package Description
    com.revature.sms.controllers
    This package contains all of the controllers that interact with the Angular front-end
    com.revature.sms.domain
    This package contains all of the domain objects, annotated to be used with Hibernate or some other JPA library
    com.revature.sms.domain.dao
    This package contains all of the DAO objects.
    com.revature.sms.domain.dto
    This package contains all of the Data Transfer Objects (DTOs).
    com.revature.sms.testLibs
    This package contains tools used by various test suites
